Notes

Subnormal numbers:
:   By default, subnormal numbers are supported.
    `max.ftz.{f16, f16x2}` flushes subnormal inputs and results to sign-preserving zero.

If values of both inputs are 0.0, then +0.0 > -0.0.

PTX ISA Notes

Introduced in PTX ISA version 7.0.

